  "detailed_description": "<h1>Coming soon - Grunn!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Frog struggles is a short action game about bugs that live in a pond, watch out for hostile bugs, water, and the big frog...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206140/extras/ce5fbea6792e02241883d9f08d7224ca.poster.avif?t=1726498073\" width=394 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206140/extras/ce5fbea6792e02241883d9f08d7224ca.webm?t=1726498073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206140/extras/ce5fbea6792e02241883d9f08d7224ca.mp4?t=1726498073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 10-20 minutes of playtime.<br></li><li> Fight other bugs with a stick.<br></li><li> Collect various pieces of fruit.<br></li><li> Become friends or foes with other tribes.<br></li><li> Big frog with a big tongue.</li></ul><br><strong>Controls</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Hold Spacebar to fly upwards.<br></li><li> WASD keys to steer.<br></li><li> Mouse buttons to attack & defend.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206140/extras/c350ac25322f0cc81d29044611c576b9.avif?t=1726498073\" width=200 height=70 /></span><br>Sokpop makes a new game every two weeks!<br>Subscribe for 3$ per month at ",
